Package fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.blueprints.io Description

Provides Blueprints' specific readers and writers used in the io module to save and persist models from external sources.

Providing efficient model import and export is tightly coupled to the database and the data representation. In order to provide this feature, a back-end module should contain an I/O specific package that overrides AbstractPersistenceHandler.
